# Normalize line endings: store LF in the repo, let Git handle the working tree.
# Without this, Windows checkouts (core.autocrlf=true) produce CRLF working trees
# that Prettier/ESLint flag repo-wide. LF keeps `npm run lint` green on every OS.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets must never be normalized.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.pdf binary
